{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1019619, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202937, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好不好不知道，只知道是一件不可能的事", "timestamp": 1612000967, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019629, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202937, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz这几天看历史，想到绝对平均主义是不对的，但是教育上的绝对平均主义呢？\n另外补充：仍然有类似现在的分流和学校好坏差异，但是完全由个人能力决定", "timestamp": 1612001067, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019643, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202937, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "请dz给出个人能力的精确定义", "timestamp": 1612001172, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019647, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202937, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: hh。dz这个人更关心对不对和好不好，至于能否实现倒不太关心。只要朝正确的方向走，走几步都是好的", "timestamp": 1612001192, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019673, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 202937, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "个人认为是好事，但是前提不可能实现", "timestamp": 1612001312, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019675, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 202937, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "后者不可能，前者更不可能", "timestamp": 1612001340, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019708, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 202937, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在其他资源不实现平均的情况下，如何实现教育资源的平均呢？所以最后还是绝对平均主义（", "timestamp": 1612001548, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019723, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202937, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "个人认为在资源有限的前提下，资源平均化对弱势群体是好事，但对整个人类不是好事；不过现在资源的集中度越来越高，超过一定程度后对整个人类也不是一件好事。", "timestamp": 1612001652, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1019732, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202937, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然这种想法可能是因为cz既不算最底层也与最高层离得很远", "timestamp": 1612001707, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 202937, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "真诚发问：\n如果全国教育资源平均化（不止是应试上的资源，还有体育，艺术，兴趣特长方面的教育资源），然后全国统一人才选拔标准。那么是不是一件好事？\n", "timestamp": 1612000926, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1612001708, "url": "", "vote": {}}}